@startuml

actor Conductor

participant "Mobile App" as App
participant "Backend API" as API
database "Database" as DB

Conductor -> App : Registrar nueva ruta
App -> API : Enviar datos de ruta
API -> DB : Guardar ruta
DB --> API : Ruta registrada
API --> App : Confirmación
App --> Conductor : Mostrar éxito

@enduml
